# Phase 8: operator-created runtime config, host manifest, and test config.
# The `infernix` binary is the sole generator of every `.dhall`; none is
# version-controlled (`infernix init` / `infernix test init` create these).
/infernix.dhall
/infernix-host.dhall
/infernix.test.dhall

